    "description": {
      "value": "<p><em>Prerequisite: 6th-level artificer</em></p>\n<p><em>Item: A suit of armor (requires attunement)</em></p>\n<p>While wearing this armor, a creature has <strong>resistance </strong>to one of the following damage types, which you choose when you infuse the item: <strong>acid</strong>, <strong>cold</strong>, <strong>fire</strong>, <strong>force</strong>, <strong>lightning</strong>, <strong>necrotic</strong>, <strong>poison</strong>, <strong>psychic</strong>, <strong>radiant</strong>, or <strong>thunder</strong>.</p>\n<section class=\"secret\">\n<p><em>DM Note:Â </em><em>Give this feature to the wearer of this Infusion and enable/edit the Passive Effect to be the chosen damage type</em><em style=\"font-family:var(--font-primary);font-size:var(--font-size-14)\">.</em></p>\n</section>",
